表格订单附件的代码预览

drop index IDX_ORDER_ID on ORDER_ATTACHMENT;

drop table if exists ORDER_ATTACHMENT;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: ORDER_ATTACHMENT */
/*==============================================================*/
create table ORDER_ATTACHMENT
(
ID int not null auto_increment,
ORDER_ID varchar(12) not null,
ATTH_TYPE char(1) not null,
ATTH_PATH varchar(128) not null,
CREATE_TIME datetime not null default CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
UPDATE_TIME datetime not null default CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
primary key (ID)
);

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: IDX_ORDER_ID */
/*==============================================================*/
create index IDX_ORDER_ID on ORDER_ATTACHMENT
(
ORDER_ID
);
